:[/b]<br/><br/>吗的半导体设备上周五走了真不敢买回来了，没有仓位心态不一样坑爹[/quote]<br/>你们这要怕死  那很简单啊  本金买了100万  涨了就卖  保持100W 跌了就继续抗 除非等到大级别位置 再涨又继续卖到100万，这样你始终这个还有100万的仓位。这样算是最怕死的做法了，而且这样跌下来会有更大的信心加仓，因为随着上涨剩余资金是越多的，反而更期望下跌补仓。这是一种心态的调整。", "lou": 241, "content_length": 266, "reply_to": 855113474, "from_client": "0 /", "postdatetimestamp": 1768808973}, {"pid": 855115016, "fid": 706, "tid": 45974302, "authorid": 150058, "type": 0, "score": 65, "score_2": 0, "recommend": 0, "postdate": "2026-01-19 15:54", "subject": "", "alterinfo": "", "content": "[quote][pid=855114371,45974302,396]Reply[/pid] [b]Post by [uid=62771233]极地丶之光[/uid] (2026-01-19 15:49):[/b]<br/><br/>狼大，实在想不出还有一轮洗筹码怎么洗，感觉大盘随时准备向上。另外3-3行情是不是还有一波指数拉高搭台子，题材唱戏的过程，率先共振指数的题材是不是能高看一眼[/quote]<br/>你是不是没出去看过现在的行情啊 今天沪深300那些还在放量压盘，航天和AI应用的家人刚逃离火场惊魂未定 指数反抽没超过昨天高点 收盘还收在5日线下，对于正常的人理解应该是大盘摇摇欲坠才是吧", "lou": 242, "content_length": 181, "reply_to": 855114371, "from_client": "0 /", "postdatetimestamp": 1768809271}, {"pid": 855115902, "fid": 706, "tid": 45974302, "authorid": 150058, "type": 0, "score": 12, "score_2": 0, "recommend": 0, "postdate": "2026-01-19 16:00", "subject": "", "alterinfo": "", "content": "[quote][pid=855115562,45974302,396]Reply[/pid] [b]Post by [uid=65247842]几脏[/uid] (2026-01-19 15:58):[/b]<br/><br/>15号麻辣粉降了10个bp，明天大概率要跟着降了[/quote]<br/>不一定，到现在来说双降的概率低于30%", "lou": 243, "content_length": 40, "reply_to": 855115562, "from_client": "0 /", "postdatetimestamp": 1768809655}, {"pid": 855134108, "fid": 706, "tid": 45974302, "authorid": 150058, "type": 0, "score": 20, "score_2": 0, "recommend": 0, "postdate": "2026-01-19 18:25", "subject": "", "alterinfo": "", "content": "[quote][pid=855133815,45974302,401]Reply[/pid] [b]Post by [uid=66905137]纵横牛熊[/uid] (2026-01-19 18:22):[/b]<br/><br/>狼大去年帖子里面明牌自己在菲利华和鼎泰的，不然帖子里面怎么那么多人也在。。<br/>我当时也买了，109多点卖掉的[/quote]<br/>我鼎泰没了  这部分钱在聚合材料里面", "lou": 244, "content_length": 37, "reply_to": 855133815, "from_client": "0 /", "postdatetimestamp": 1768818319}, {"pid": 855135136, "fid": 706, "tid": 45974302, "authorid": 150058, "type": 0, "score": 17, "score_2": 0, "recommend": 0, "postdate": "2026-01-19 18:36", "subject": "", "alterinfo": "", "content": "[quote][pid=855134799,45974302,401]Reply[/pid] [b]Post by [uid=66907545]ptydd[/uid] (2026-01-19 18:32):[/b]<br/><br/>狼大，液冷这块今年不参与了吗，谢谢&amp;#128591;[/quote]<br/>我不是发了我持仓了么  英维克锁了", "lou": 245, "content_length": 35, "reply_to": 855134799, "from_client": "0 /", "postdatetimestamp": 1768818966}, {"pid": 855137529, "fid": 706, "tid": 45974302, "authorid": 150058, "type": 0, "score": 103, "score_2": 0, "recommend": 0, "postdate": "2026-01-19 18:59", "subject": "", "alterinfo": "", "content": "我觉得大家应该很游刃有余才对啊  等别人来拥抱推高，要么加速上去吃完，要么产生分歧下来又能补仓<br/>这不是一根筋两头通吗？只有没持仓的人才急吧<br/>还是说大家怕挣钱？", "lou": 246, "content_length": 150, "from_client": "0 /", "postdatetimestamp": 1768820370}, {"pid": 855137922, "fid": 706, "tid": 45974302, "authorid": 150058, "type": 0, "score": 13, "score_2": 0, "recommend": 0, "postdate": "2026-01-19 19:03", "subject": "", "alterinfo": "", "content": "[quote][pid=855137833,45974302,402]Reply[/pid] [b]Post by [uid=38881553]Peace Maker[/uid] (2026-01-19 19:02):[/b]<br/><br/>哈？狼大来掩膜版了？不来路维光电 清溢光电吗[/quote]<br/>什么叫我来掩模版了  你问问图图他们 这个票谁做上去的", "lou": 247, "content_length": 53, "reply_to": 855137833, "from_client": "0 /", "postdatetimestamp": 1768820601}, {"pid": 855138672, "fid": 706, "tid": 45974302, "authorid": 150058, "type": 0, "score": 73, "score_2": 0, "recommend": 0, "postdate": "2026-01-19 19:11", "subject": "", "alterinfo": "", "content": "[quote][pid=855138372,45974302,402]Reply[/pid] [b]Post by [uid=38881553]Peace Maker[/uid] (2026-01-19 19:08):[/b]<br/><br/>狼大来清溢光电拉一把，让我把成本做做~~~~~[s:ac:花痴][/quote]<br/>你们是不是觉得我不会收割人？", "lou": 248, "content_length": 33, "reply_to": 855138372, "from_client": "0 /", "postdatetimestamp": 1768821108}, {"pid": 855175863, "fid": 706, "tid": 45974302, "authorid": 150058, "type": 0, "score": 91, "score_2": 0, "recommend": 0, "postdate": "2026-01-20 08:46", "subject": "", "alterinfo": "", "content": "[quote][pid=855175334,45974302,407]Reply[/pid] [b]Post by [uid=67063452]Halcyonn[/uid] (2026-01-20 08:41):[/b]<br/><br/>今天期指，300多空单都减的好多(多单占优)，其他空单占优[/quote]<br/>对 所以你有什么思考<br/>既然你愿意学习 我给你我的思考作为参考，不一定对<br/><br/>因为前两天都是GJD主动打压沪深300，那通过期指看是不是今天可能GJD反而是要兜底沪深300来拖指数，那用金融的兜底的概率会比较大。而这样就有可能出现二八分化的场景，所以谨慎对小盘做加仓的T，特别是如果开盘后出现白线在上的情况下。 这就是一个情况的对应思路。", "lou": 249, "content_length": 314, "reply_to": 855175334, "from_client": "0 /", "postdatetimestamp": 1768870014}, {"pid": 855177793, "fid": 706, "tid": 45974302, "authorid": 150058, "type": 0, "score": 39, "score_2": 0, "recommend": 0, "postdate": "2026-01-20 09:06", "subject": "", "alterinfo": "", "content": "[quote][pid=855177518,45974302,408]Reply[/pid] [b]Post by [uid=67063452]Halcyonn[/uid] (2026-01-20 09:03):[/b]<br/><br/>谢谢狼大解答，好开心[s:pst:亲]，股市每天都给题目，感觉回到了上学时候的数学课堂，总希望能答题正确[s:ac:哭笑]，狼大就是数学老师的感觉。昨天金融拿znz来说，确实是个低位机会，直接下冲到12月5日的主力线，但是昨日金融和今天对金融的作用没想到。[/quote]<br/>主要是今天LPR出来了 确实没动，那根据十五五开年，所以预期第一季度要调的情况下，年后那个月降息概率就很高，而根据金融目前走法已经是反映了1月不会双降的情况，那接下来就只要预期3月能降就可以了。", "lou": 250, "content_length": 192, "reply_to": 855177518, "from_client": "0 /", "postdatetimestamp": 1768871172}, {"pid": 855187305, "fid": 706, "tid": 45974302, "authorid": 150058, "type": 0, "score": 65, "score_2": 0, "recommend": 0, "postdate": "2026-01-20 10:20", "subject": "", "alterinfo": "", "content": "今天这个感觉像是融资盘爆仓的状态 谨慎接盘 等国家队看用什么兜底 在哪里兜底", "lou": 251, "content_length": 70, "from_client": "0 /", "postdatetimestamp": 1768875610}, {"pid": 855190799, "fid": 706, "tid": 45974302, "authorid": 150058, "type": 0, "score": 43, "score_2": 0, "recommend": 0, "postdate": "2026-01-20 10:42", "subject": "", "alterinfo": "", "content": "[quote][pid=855190659,45974302,422]Reply[/pid] [b]Post by [uid=65329649]zippo578[/uid] (2026-01-20 10:41):[/b]<br/><br/>楼里应该没人割肉吧[s:ac:哭笑][/quote]<br/>这都ETF才2个点的波动 我都不懂操作空间在哪", "lou": 252, "content_length": 45, "reply_to": 855190659, "from_client": "0 /", "postdatetimestamp": 1768876942}, {"pid": 855191725, "fid": 706, "tid": 45974302, "authorid": 150058, "type": 0, "score": 39, "score_2": 0, "recommend": 0, "postdate": "2026-01-20 10:48", "subject": "", "alterinfo": "", "content": "[quote][pid=855191069,45974302,423]Reply[/pid] [b]Post by [uid=65329649]zippo578[/uid] (2026-01-20 10:44):[/b]<br/><br/>已开启磕头战法[s:ac:瞎][/quote]<br/>国家队兜底了  没什么大问题的。今天金融三驾马车都是兜底了的。而且今天是在两融部分爆仓出了一些恐慌盘的量的情况下，我觉得这里控得蛮稳的<br/>不激进就没事。日内低点我都没加，我等回暖", "lou": 253, "content_length": 175, "reply_to": 855191069, "from_client": "0 /", "postdatetimestamp": 1768877309}, {"pid": 855192311, "fid": 706, "tid": 45974302, "authorid": 150058, "type": 0, "score": 7, "score_2": 0, "recommend": 0, "postdate": "2026-01-20 10:52", "subject": "", "alterinfo": "", "content": "[quote][pid=855192062,45974302,425]Reply[/pid] [b]Post by [uid=43198491]真伪善者查尔斯[/uid] (2026-01-20 10:50):[/b]<br/><br/>狼大这新头像是麦晓雯联动的那个明日方舟角色么 叫啥来着，维什戴尔好像[/quote]<br/>不知道啊 不是我弄的", "lou": 254, "content_length": 23, "reply_to": 855192062, "from_client": "0 /", "postdatetimestamp": 1768877534}, {"pid": 855193678, "fid": 706, "tid": 45974302, "authorid": 150058, "type": 0, "score": 52, "score_2": 0, "recommend": 0, "postdate": "2026-01-20 11:01", "subject": "", "alterinfo": "", "content": "金融继续增量护盘。所以你们知道复盘的想法有啥用了吗", "lou": 255, "content_length": 50, "from_client": "0 /", "postdatetimestamp": 1768878074}, {"pid": 855195045, "fid": 706, "tid": 45974302, "authorid": 150058, "type": 0, "score": 51, "score_2": 0, "recommend": 0, "postdate": "2026-01-20 11:10", "subject": "", "alterinfo": "[E1768878704 0 0]\t", "content": "[quote][pid=855194658,45974302,427]Reply[/pid] [b]Post by [uid=9032340]letuswowing[/uid] (2026-01-20 11:08):[/b]<br/><br/>狼大 感觉下午还要踩一下低点 不破的话是不是就算这几天的底部了[/quote]<br/>反正目前看技术上在做3-3日K级别的第一次二买位 主要还是看GJD兜底位置和用什么东西兜底 不然低点对了 买错板块不SB了？<br/>就比如我说12月中旬之后都不做AI硬，不也是这么多满仓在里面哀嚎的，也不懂为什么这么头铁", "lou": 256, "content_length": 198, "reply_to": 855194658, "from_client": "0 /", "postdatetimestamp": 1768878657}, {"pid": 855195719, "fid": 706, "tid": 45974302, "authorid": 150058, "type": 0, "score": 36, "score_2": 0, "recommend": 0, "postdate": "2026-01-20 11:15", "subject": "", "alterinfo": "", "content": "你们看航天里面的，融资爆仓的要卖出来，柚子要卖出来，散户也在犹豫种卖出来，除了一波接盘资金，后面根本没有钱继续接了<br/>所以吃那种短线战法的必须速度要快 要准，否则也会变成坐牢的一员", "lou": 257, "content_length": 174, "from_client": "0 /", "postdatetimestamp": 1768878901}, {"pid": 855195908, "fid": 706, "tid": 45974302, "authorid": 150058, "type": 0, "score": 16, "score_2": 0, "recommend": 0, "postdate": "2026-01-20 11:16", "subject": "", "alterinfo": "", "content": "[quote][pid=855195570,45974302,428]Reply[/pid] [b]Post by [uid=66515200]arikon[/uid] (2026-01-20 11:14):[/b]<br/><br/>[/quote]<br/>去哪？我之前不是分享过了么  机构的钱只在机构趋势里面轮动 除非像之前白酒那种或者新能源牛市那种，不然目前科技牛市他轮动去哪里？", "lou": 258, "content_length": 127, "reply_to": 855195570, "from_client": "0 /", "postdatetimestamp": 1768878970}, {"pid": 855196581, "fid": 706, "tid": 45974302, "authorid": 150058, "type": 0, "score": 26, "score_2": 0, "recommend": 0, "postdate": "2026-01-20 11:20", "subject": "", "alterinfo": "", "content": "[quote][pid=855195701,45974302,428]Reply[/pid] [b]Post by [uid=66983776]大时代冲冲冲[/uid] (2026-01-20 11:14):[/b]<br/><br/>因为大伙刚学会拥抱主线，刚了解到AI硬是整个牛市的主线，不想挪窝了哈哈哈。<br/>还有没有想象到主线板块之间能差异这么大[/quote]<br/>我之前还去别的帖子也提了一嘴，说接下来半导体设备比AI硬要好  毕竟是预判 出现了才确认我说的对", "lou": 259, "content_length": 93, "reply_to": 855195701, "from_client": "0 /", "postdatetimestamp": 1768879231}], "__T": {"fid": 706, "tid": 45974302, "topic_misc": null, "subject": "自立自强，科学技术打头阵", "locked": 0, "recommend": 0, "quote_to": null, "quote_from": 0, "type": 36, "replies": 155484, "authorid": 150058, "postdate": 1768179906, "lastpost": 1782109184, "jdata": null, "author": "-阿狼-", "lastposter": "zippo578", "digest": 0, "lastmodify": 1782109203, "tpid": 0, "post_misc_var": {"content_length": 412, "fid": 706, "comment_id": ",854270755,860174433", "14": {"17": 1, "14": 4, "13": 4, "12": 1}, "16": "63335896,19412700,26652007,67067074,20672033,66881586,67068843,66199622,60819388,60409766,67057614,60264977,61082281,42701832,6